# Generate a Python CLI quiz app that loads the questions

@model gpt-4o

@role :coder(Python)

@context file: questions.json

@task {
  Write a Python CLI quiz app that:
  1. Loads questions from questions.json
  2. Asks each question one at a time, showing the options
  3. Accepts user input (A/B/C/D)
  4. Shows if they're right or wrong, with the explanation
  5. Tracks score and prints the final result at the end

  Only output the code.
}

@constraint Use only the standard library.
@constraint Keep it under 80 lines.

@output format: python, file: quiz.py
